    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite the COU-level decision of Not Accepted for regulatory submission, the credibility assessment package itself is accepted as a complete and valid documentation artifact. The assessment transparently identifies all 13 credibility factor gaps, documents achieved versus required levels for MRL 5, and provides a well-supported evidentiary basis for the Not Accepted regulatory outcome. The package satisfies the documentation requirements for a Minimal profile UnitOfAssurance and is accepted as a credibility evidence record.",
